com.siemens.ct.exi
Interface EXIBodyDecoder

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractEXIBodyDecoder, EXIBodyDecoderInOrder, EXIBodyDecoderInOrderSC, EXIBodyDecoderReordered
public interface EXIBodyDecoder

Internal EXI Decoder interface to transform an EXI stream back to XML Infoset entities.

Version:
0.7
Author:
Daniel.Peintner.EXT@siemens.com, Joerg.Heuer@siemens.com
